data.description: If you missed this one before you have a 2nd chance! Wonderful Regency built home only 5 years old ready for new memories to be made. 3 bedrooms down with 4th/Bonus up. Lots of storage with large closets and walk in attic space. Hardwood floor throughout, split floor plan, tall ceilings, open kitchen w/ breakfast bar, granite countertops in kitchen and bath, wood fenced yard with patio. All systems still under 5 years old. Low taxes. Convenient access to Oakland shops, restaurants and more.
